nodes.text: This garage owner lived on Klatooine, who acquired the Klatooinian Barada from his parents. Barada was sold due to being a disrespectful child and became the garage owner's indentured servant.
At a later date, the owner was challenged by Jabba the Hutt to a game of sabacc. Jabba rigged the game, and the garage owner soon lost both his garage and Barada.
